        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] pt-4">Build Your Greatest Playing XI</h3>
        <p>
          Every cricket fan has asked the question: <strong>What is the greatest playing XI of all time?</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          16-0play allows you to answer that question by building your own ultimate cricket team. Choose from legendary players, modern superstars, and all-time greats to create a balanced and powerful squad capable of dominating the competition.
        </p>
        <p>
          Success isn't just about selecting the highest-rated players. You'll need to balance batting depth, bowling strength, all-rounders, team chemistry, and strategic combinations. Every selection matters when you're chasing a perfect season.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're building a team around explosive batters, world-class bowlers, or legendary all-rounders, your decisions will determine whether your team becomes a champion—or falls short of greatness.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] pt-4">Experience the Ultimate Cricket Strategy Challenge</h3>
        <p>
          16-0play is more than a traditional cricket simulator. It's a cricket strategy game where every match matters.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your objective is simple: <strong>Win 16 matches. Lose none.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          Throughout your season, you'll face difficult opponents, changing conditions, pressure situations, and strategic decisions that test your ability to build and manage a winning team. Every victory brings you one step closer to cricket immortality. Can your team handle the pressure of a perfect run?
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] pt-4">Compete for the Best Record</h3>
        <p>
          The challenge doesn't end with building a great team. Every player competes for a place on the global leaderboard. Track your season record, compare your results with other players, and discover who has built the greatest cricket team. Whether you finish with a respectable 10-6 record or achieve a legendary unbeaten season, every campaign becomes part of your story. The ultimate goal remains the same: <strong>Go 16-0.</strong>
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] pt-4">Inspired by the World's Biggest Cricket Competitions</h3>
        <p>
          16-0play captures the excitement, unpredictability, and strategic depth that make franchise cricket so compelling. Fans who follow major T20 tournaments, cricket standings, schedules, scores, and player performances will feel right at home. Our game combines the thrill of competitive cricket with deep strategic gameplay, creating an experience that appeals to casual fans and cricket enthusiasts alike.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] pt-4">Every Season Tells a Different Story</h3>
        <p>
          No two seasons are ever the same. One season, your star batter may carry your team to glory. The next, a surprise underdog could derail your perfect run. Momentum, team balance, tactical decisions, and a bit of luck all play a role in determining your final record. Will you play aggressively and chase dominance? Or will you build a balanced squad capable of surviving the pressure of a perfect season? The path to 16-0 is never easy.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] pt-4">Can You Achieve the Perfect Season?</h3>
        <p>
          Thousands of teams can win matches. Very few can become legends.
        </p>
        <p>
          Build your greatest playing XI, test your strategy, climb the leaderboard, and attempt the ultimate challenge in cricket gaming: <strong>Create the greatest cricket team ever assembled and complete the perfect 16-0 season.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          Your journey starts now.
        </p>
